    bottomLine: 'Pick Klaviyo if you are a serious e-commerce store ($200K+ revenue) wanting the most powerful customer-data platform. Pick Omnisend if you want Klaviyo-like features at lower cost for smaller stores. Pick beehiiv if you are a newsletter creator monetising via subscriptions or sponsorships. Pick ActiveCampaign for SMB B2B marketing automation. Pick Mailchimp for SMB simplicity. Pick Mailerlite if budget is the primary constraint. Most teams should run exactly one email platform; switching costs are real and the differentiation between tools is workflow fit, not capability gaps.',
