        slug: 'claude',
        whyPicked: 'Claude (Anthropic) is the AI assistant teachers reach for when writing quality matters - rubric design, parent communication drafts, lesson plan structuring, IEP language, and feedback to students. The 200K token context handles entire textbook chapters and student work bundles. Claude defaults to a measured, thoughtful tone that matches educational writing better than ChatGPT. Free tier is generous for daily teacher use.',
